room_title: Escape room "The Eventide Departure" by Puzzle Break in Seattle
room_description:
Can you and your companions find the clues, solve the mystery of the last will and testament of the recently departed Professor Firestone, and escape the seance before time runs out?
Featuring: Revolutionary dueling escape option for two teams of 2-5 players! Massive new Seattle Puzzle Break location features two digitally-connected copies of The Eventide Departure. Unravel the mystery alone with your team, or go head-to-head against rival adventurers!
